tatami.jade

Class JadeAgentWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • jade.core.Agent
      • tatami.jade.JadeAgentWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    jade.core.TimerListener, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, PlatformLoader.PlatformLink

    public class JadeAgentWrapper
extends jade.core.Agent
implements PlatformLoader.PlatformLink
    A wrapper for an AgentManager instance, that wraps it inside a Jade Agent.

    When started as a Jade agent, the wrapper is supposed to receive one argument: the AgentManager instance.

    Author:
    Andrei Olaru
